3.\tab Confirm that C:\\TLOHome\\apps\\Windows contains tlo-ggi.exe, tlo-gi.exe, tlo-tag.exe, tlo-gsi.exe, and search-artist-db.exe.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af14\afs22\alang1025 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe1033\hich\af2\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa200\ltrpar\hyphpar0\f2\fs20\cf0\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af11\langfe1033\fi-360\li360\lin360\sb0\sa0{\loch
