Search-path outputs: bootlist.csv is caret-delimited and uses a Show and VolumePath layout. Older four-column rows can still be read where present, but new output writes Show^VolumePath.}\cell\row\pard \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af14\afs22\alang1025 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe1033\hich\af2\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa200\ltrpar\hyphpar0\f2\fs20\cf0\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af11\langfe1033\sl252\slmult1\sb0\sa80\loch

